string.name: css_light
string.Data: <style type="text/css"> html {overflow-x: hidden;} img {margin-left:-5px; margin-right:5px; width:310; height:50;} a {color: #417bf9; text-decoration: underline;}abbr {border-bottom-style: none; color: #009900; cursor: help; font-style: italic; } em {font-style: italic;}p {color: #222222; font-size: %dpt;}span {color: #666666;} abbr {text-decoration: none;} .acute {font-size: %dpt;} </style>
